metadata.name: TOMATOZ #1
metadata.description: Did you know the probability of winning the 6-digit lottery is 1 in 13,983,816, Tomatoz - Heheland is a collection of 9999 Tomatoz created to give a better opportunity to own Potatoz (Memeland) to those who missed out.  We are spending most of the money from the Mint and 90% Royalty buying Potatoz from the secondary market and raffle them off to all Tomatoz Army.
